dqm.jku.trustkg.dsd

Class DSDKnowledgeGraph

  • java.lang.Object
    • dqm.jku.trustkg.dsd.DSDKnowledgeGraph

  • public class DSDKnowledgeGraph
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    Lisa, optimusseptim Wrapper class for the entire KG to manage multiple data sources and their connections. Allows to automatically annotate data profiles for multiple data sources, persist, or export the KG.
